    "markings": "Impressed on top side of metal heel: [in script] \"Silver Streak\" (2) Impressed on bottom side of metal heel: \"SAUNDERS SINCE 1858 \/ MODEL 1038 \/ 1000 WATTS \/ 110-120 VOLTS A.C. ONLY\" (3) Molded in Pyrex below handle: \"PYREX\"",
    "signed": null,
